# Fuzz
# The cargo-fuzz build directory is transient.
fuzz/target/
# `fuzz/artifacts/` holds raw crash/timeout/oom reproducers that cargo-fuzz
# writes when a target crashes. They are transient dumps; once a crash is
# triaged its (minimized) reproducer is copied into `fuzz/corpus/<target>/`
# and committed so it becomes a permanent, replayed regression case.
fuzz/artifacts/
# NOTE: `fuzz/corpus/` is intentionally NOT ignored. It is the retained
# regression corpus (R38.4): committed crash reproducers and seeds that
# `cargo fuzz run <target>` replays on every run.

# Logs / temp
*.log
tmp/
.kiro/tmp-*

# Kiro spec/workspace metadata — local only, never publish
.kiro/
